76561197999419093,Recommended,238430,11952224,"Posted: 1 September, 2014",all,Ѕᴏᴜᴎᴅᴡᴀᴠᴇ™,"Contagion is a fun interesting twist on the zombie survival horror genre. It has multiple modes to play which include Escape, Extraction, Panic, Hunted, etc. In each mode you generally start off as a survivor, though sometimes you do start as a zombie. Your mission: to survive as long as possible. Once you die you get to control a zombie and attack the other survivors. It can be a really fun experience, though at times it can be somewhat boring due in large part to how big the maps are. After playing all the modes I think I like Extraction the best since it has alot of AI zombies along with the player controlled ones. That and the survivors have to hold out at certain locations which makes finding them easy. Oh yeah, and zombies have special abilities unique to them. For $4.99(as of 9/1/14) it's definitely worth it! The developer has already said that ALL future DLC will be free of charge. That's a pretty good deal!"
