,Recommended,238430,19334696,"Posted: 28 November, 2015",all,Shadow Dee,"What makes this Game specialDon't ever compare it with Left4Dead2.You can compare some of the gamemodes and teamplay but overall, Contagion is much more realistic and L4D2 more the oldschool arcade type.Here are some differences:Any different Zombie species?L4D2yeah, loads of with different abilitiesContagionno, only normal and armored policemen, just differs from NPC (no special abilities except crawling) or player controlled (able to crawl, to blend, to build a horde and special vision)How to kill a Zombie?L4D2pump 'em full of leadContagionheadshots are a one-hit-kill and therefore key to survival, because a bodyshot does much less damage, means it takes alot more ammo and ammo is sparseGetting wounded/killed by a zombie means...L4D2wounded...it slows you down, killed...you're dead (unless a teammate helps you up)Contagionwounded...you'll probably turn into one of 'em, killed...you'll turnWhat about the User Interface?L4D2displayed health and inventory of you and your teammates, cursorContagiononly your health, stamina and inventory (teammates displayed by holding tab), no cursor, map and notifications on the phone (equipped by tapping B)How's the weapon handling?L4D2fire arms: no aiming (except sniper rifle) instead there's punching with weapon, melee: chargable punch from upContagionfire arms: aiming for every weapon (punch with weapon by tapping V), melee: chargable punch from up(LMB) and the side(RMB)other differencesother gamemodes like extraction (your team has to escort NPC  survivors) or hide'n'seek with player controlled Zombiesthere's a PvP mode for survivors (last survivor wins)ammo and weapons can be found anywhere, mostly where you least expect itthere's no storylinesome character animations a bit poor but hopefully getting better with the next patchesAs you read, it differs from L4D2.But I can't say that one is better than the other because they're different. I really enjoy playing L4D2 when I'm looking for fast-paced oldschool arcade fps action. But when I'm in the mood for a realistic Zombie-experience, I choose Contagion over all for the time being.ConclusionIt's a realistic Zombiegame where you can also play as a Zombie in any gamemode.I rate it 82/100Also check out the wikiahttp://contagion-game.wikia.com/wiki/Contagion_Game_WikiThank you for reading the whole review.I hope it was helpful for most of you.Feel free to comment if you have a question about the game or the reviewDominik"
