,Recommended,238430,9826511,"Posted: 15 April, 2014",all,Crom The Beast,"A fun zombie shooter with slower undead. With the 3 modes given it's a good time with friends. You can play a campaign escape mode where you follow objectives through your cell. A hunted mode which is a last man standing deathmatch with the undead roaming about on sizable maps where death isn't the end. You will come back as the undead to hunt down the remaining survivors while rallying other zombies behind you. Finally, you have an escape mode where you need to get to a pickup point on your GPS, and fight off hordes until you can escape.Overall it's a fun alternative if you're a fan of their older free mod of ""Zombic Panic Source"" available if you own Half Life 2. Of course Left 4 Dead reigns supreme for the zombie survival genre with pals, but this is a great title if you're into the growing zombie trend."
