,Recommended,238430,10946642,"Posted: 29 June, 2014",all,TrapsAreGay,"Finally a zombie game that does zombies right, despite some bugs. Occasionally they will get themselves stuck on a street sign or crouch awkwardly but they are dumb zombies after all so I give them slack.The lighting and audio is great.The amount of ammo is just enough where you will run out if youre trigger happy but always have enough if you use wisely. Sometimes though it seems like 1/4 of your shots are duds: perfectly aimed shots will somehow miss.Also as said by many already there should be more maps.Zombie players are simply overpowered if they know what they are doing, they move too fast and deal damage too fast. Too many times I had to play dodge the bullet with a player zombie, and lost half the time. Keep a shotgun or automatic for them.Melee weapons are a bit wonky. Keep distance while using and only use right click, left click appears to be useless as it takes about 10 hits for a kill, while right click takes 1 or 2.In short, great concept and look, but needs some work. I think they may have released it a bit early, but they are still working on it. Only buy if it's your cup of tea. Please note the date of this review as things may change in the future."
