,Recommended,238430,16254668,"Posted: 7 June, 2015",all,Punitious,9/11
,Recommended,238430,9826138,"Posted: 15 April, 2014",all,Cpt. John Stalky,"So lets start from beginning. Zombie apocalypse come to the city of Roanoke. And only you and other seven survivors must find a way out from this madness.Contagion is a indie co-op game where you can play as survivor or as a zombie. Contagion is the next generation of two Zombie Panic games. Developers tried to put everything that was not in Zombie panic, including better graphic and more cooperative missions.Game got three gamemodes each with different goals.Lets start with Escape mod. This mod is just only about escaping a group of survivor from infested area. The whole team must communicate to each other to finish the mission. And there is a BIG disadvantage with cooperation. Most people won´t cooperate or listen to you and well without communication you lose for sure. And well also you for finishing this mod you need to use your cell phone and read messages from other characters.Another mod is Extraction. In this mod group of survivors must find AI survivors in the map. Thanks to cellphone you can be navigated by GPS to find position of survivors. This mod is also about cooperating with other folks. Without them you can get really easier overwhelmed. Disadvantage is that AI of survivors is pretty stupid in some situations.The last mod of this game is Hunted. This is pure PvP mod where survivors hunt each other. When you die you will turn into a zombie and continue hunting a living persons. The last man standing won.Thats all about survivors. I mentioned that you can play as a zombie character. Mostly in every gamemode you can play as zombie. Well you become zombie when you got infected or died by zombies or players.Well this game got pros and nons. So far it is Indie game and well developers did their best to make their game playable, but well without co-op and communication to each other you don´t have chance and for some people it could be frustating.Well in my opinion game is good but still need some improvements.Thats why my rate is 8/10"
