76561198084480105,Recommended,238430,7863312,"Posted: 1 December, 2013",all,roy8892,"oh great another zombie game right? well yes but with a much needed refreshment to gameplay style. first and foremost obviously this game is still in the early beta stage and it is very obvious in many ways in the game, but the amazing thing is, it is still so much fun! the biggest thing you will notice first is the importance of shot accuracy. hitting these guys in the chest and limbs does almost nothing forcing you to slow down from random fast paced shooting like most fps games, and actually pace yourself and make those headshots like a zombie game should be. doing that, while also keeping yourself from getting pinned down in a corner can be quite a lot harder then you would expect, but boy is it a lot of fun. now while quite a lot of fun to play, it has also proven to me to be quite frustrating. for instance, when you are a zombie, there is no way of knowing where the other human players are except by listening for there gunshots. this is very difficult and very frustrating leavng you just wondering around helplessly for quite some time. and gltiches seem to be very common so far, but that is to be expected considering it is a beta after all. on a 1 to 10 scale, id have to say right now its a 6. but considering how early on this game still is, thats extremely impressive! cant wait to see more improvements guys! keep up the good work"
