,Recommended,238430,13813556,"Posted: 3 January, 2015",all,tedzza,"Contagion is a fantastic game with amazing graphics, immersive gameplay and a sense of terror that you can never shake off.This game is not your average zombie shooter game, it is an intense survival game that is best played in a team with friends. Watch as you struggle to survive, using whatever is around you to keep you and/or your team safe. Move from building to building, reinforcing each one until it gets broken down by the infected.This game also adds a new perspective to zombie survival games. When in multiplayer, instead of dying, you become one of the infected. Your aim is no longer to survive, it is to kill the surviving.There are a range of maps, gamemodes and characters to choose from which gives you a completely different experience each time you play."
