ia bs) but youll press it and turn it back off by the time it actually does turn on thinking you missed the key. The whole control set up is ♥♥♥♥ing awful... if you want to play it for longer than I have, you'll have to remap the keys. You got this dumb cellphone, which tells you everytime someone walks through a door. Sometimes you have it going off literally every second to read some dumb message. The process of switching to your cellphone turns off your flashlight(dumb) even if you're carrying a (dumber) pocket flashlight. Switching to your cell phone is done by pressing b...right next to your melee key v... and your drop key g... and your flashlight key f... q sometimes switches to the cellphone but not all the time... so you're gunna be throwing your gun away trying to do any of those other tasks....gameplay, youre just gunna be running after the person who knows the way picking up their scraps, or if your the person who knows the way youre just running ahead of everyone to get the guns... and youll end up using your machete the whole time anyways.. feeling like you have another hour of gameplay to go but really you have another 30 seconds... yeah now that Ive thought about it... this game is actually really terrible. Get left 4 dead1 2... get no room left in hell... making it to the train in no room left in hell feels good, you say to yourself ""Wow, I ♥♥♥♥ing made it yeah all right!"" this game you make it to the train and its more like ""ok... that was totally unsatisfying"" Don't even bother with this game on sale... seriously."
